Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:06.75,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:09.05,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:17.07,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:26.49,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:29.96,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.06,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:55.32,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:12.96,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.21,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:22.07,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:27.97,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.51,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:41.72,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:46.06,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:49.04,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.85,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.60,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:54.17,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.83,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.45,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.96,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.62,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:01.69,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:05.89,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.63,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.17,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.52,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:25.80,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:32.72,DefaultLow,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered\Njust before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around\Nthe world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered\Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To reach Fish-Man Island,\NLuffy and company found themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,looking for a coating craftsman\Non the Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, also on the archipelago\Nare the Celestial Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,world nobles powerful enough\Nto hold sway over Navy Headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and formidable rookies\Nheaded for the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm worried about\Nthe old craftsman guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if he's in such a rough town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's 100 times\Nstronger than you kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Target is Camie!! The Looming\NClutches of a Professional Kidnapper"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,\Nthe navy is obviously aware
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that big-name rookies\Nhave made landfall here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, does that mean there's\Nno telling when they might strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this is another\Ncase of rookie's luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe Navy HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,probably has its hands full\Nwith something else right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless something especially\Nproblematic happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they won't waste major military\Nresources on things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, to be more precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take care not to cause\Nany trouble." Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go find the\Nold coating craftsman now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's hoping you do find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here! Sabaody Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even trying\Nto find the old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that lady did say\Nhe likes this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only if we couldn't find him\Nin the lawless area!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The Ferris wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it from\Nthis close before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys! Let's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you're not trying to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie! You are forbidden to go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely forbid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's moving at quite\Na leisurely pace indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a truly wonderful view!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:06:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you scared, Camie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really scary, but really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's still beating so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing! I was in the very front!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went so fast my head\Nalmost wound up behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought my heart\Nwas going to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentle rides like this\Nare more my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a delightful view...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spin too much, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin! Spin! Spin! Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin! Spin! Spin! Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin! Spin! Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:08:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots spun too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! We're so high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're selling\Nice cream, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For reals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Everyone's so tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ocean! The ocean, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how it looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you happy enough to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've always dreamed of this,\Never since I was a little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been so high up before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cherish this memory forever!\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin and Pappagu\Nonly let me come here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you guys are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.10,0:10:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams as a kid\Nhave come back to life too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merfolk and fish-men always dream\Nof coming here when growing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gondola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never thought they'd\Nbe that strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you had it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's this proposition of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Peterman-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the girl that was with\NStraw Hat Luffy might be a mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Camie! Pappagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When her shoe came off,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a tail fin instead of a foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But these strong companions of hers\Nsound like trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, a mermaid on land\Nis a golden opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're impossible to catch\Nin the water, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for telling me, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the info, you can have\N10% of her selling price.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Actually, we were\Nhoping more like 20%...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:13:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, 10% is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here a minute, Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Choose something yummy for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High Priest Urouge. Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Dragon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think they'd swagger about the\Nlawless area with nary a care...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only choice is to kneel\Nand let him pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth could Shalria\Nand Father have gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving me behind like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do know their final destination,\Nso please rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you walk like a turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also sway too much and\Nmake for a horrible ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You irritate me to no end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:15:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you moving?! You're humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! Please overlook this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's losing blood and needs urgent care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a race against time!\NThe hospital is just ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is very bad, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you must be swift...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and be out of your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be out of your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:16:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about utterly selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important,\Ncourtesy toward me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or a commoner's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commoners owe their existence\Nto the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm making you my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall arrange to send her\Nto the Holy Land as your 13th wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I'm tired of\Nwives #1 through #5 now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sending them back\Nto the commoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my fiancée!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up in front of me, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You murderer! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're even more screwed up\Nthan the rumors say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her on ahead to the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Apoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's an East Blue pirate hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he walkin'\Nin the middle of the street?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he know anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna cause trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need directions or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to die, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay still, guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stood up to a Celestial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's only natural that you died!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've sworn he managed\Nto dodge my shots...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you get in the way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't gimme that, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to attract\Nan admiral to these islands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomato juice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a pirate, you must know\Nsome of the unwritten pirate rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get us caught up in your trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wasn't there a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even listenin' to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You alright in the head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I'm not hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about on the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A genuine dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to avoid the worst-case\Nscenario thanks to Jewelry Bonney...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is Pirate Hunter Zoro,\Na member of the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard their crew's crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but attacking a Celestial Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural he was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the shadow of death\Nupon him at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard unleashed an absurd\Namount of bloodlust for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worth 120 million,\Nyet only #2 on his ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem like the type\Nto play second fiddle to anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess that goes to show\Nthe caliber of his captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Where's the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta take him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about 'im! He's a total stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate that helps people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't ever heard of that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked into town earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw some bubble bicycle\Nthings flying around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I saw! They're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's buy some!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to see how nice they ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Nami-sa--!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, they have so\Nmany kinds of ice cream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we got so caught up in it all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you freaking out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji?! It's really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not following you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down first! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie's been kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kidnapping team probably did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno why, but they let people\Nsell merfolk and fish-men
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they aren't bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie's gonna get sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gonna be a slave forever\Nand it's all our fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of Human Shoppes\Non these islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there's no telling\Nwhen or where she'll be sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know who kidnapped her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The archipelago is too big,\Nbut for now let's all split up and...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.94,0:22:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us exactly where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.74,0:22:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are pros\Nwhen it comes to this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling the Flying Fish Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.99,0:23:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Eh?!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one will go for quite a price!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.51,0:23:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite lively, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's welcome our \Ncustomers and start the auction!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sure to get a lot of high bids!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue Camie The Archipelago's\NLingering Dark History
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
